Vice President

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE Limited is pleased to present the opportunity to lease 3.51 acres of industrial land on a high exposure corner of Lickman Road and Progress Way. A short 2 minute drive north if the Trans Canada Highway at Exit 116, a major freeway interchange suitable for the traveling public and a major trucking hub. Offering excellent street exposure on 3 sides, this desirable location is a short 25 minute drive to the US/Canada border and 100km east of Vancouver.

The property offers a rare opportunity to secure one acre of secure yard space, along with approximately 3,500 square feet of turn-key office space. The property fronts Highway 1 and offers a desirable signage opportunity. This is an ideal opportunity for users with high parking requirements, equipment sales and rental, transportation companies, lay-down yard requirements, and more.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FOR LEASE | HIGH EXPOSURE OFFICE & YARD OPPORTUNITY
